    "body": "Can we re-open this? \r\n\r\n`epoll` was introduced in [glibc 2.3.2](http://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man7/epoll.7.html#VERSIONS), manylinux1 supports [`glibc <= 2.5`](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0513/#the-manylinux1-policy) so it should be possible to enable epoll without breaking manylinux1 compatibility."
  },
